message.entry: The input must be real-valued, with a built-in floating-point datatype (double or single).
The input must be a column vector with a length that is a multiple of the number of columns in ''ParityCheckMatrix.''
Multiframe decoding is not compatible with an Iteration Termination Condition of ''Parity check satisfied''.
The parity-check matrix must be a sparse matrix.
The parity-check matrix must have at least one column.
The parity-check matrix must have more columns than rows.
The parity-check matrix must be a zero-one matrix.
The parity-check matrix must have at least one nonzero element in each column.
The parity-check matrix must have at least one nonzero element in each row.
